    <refpurpose> A statistics toolbox.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
    Stixbox is a statistics toolbox which provides distribution functions, datasets,
    statistical tests and plotting facilities.
    </para>

    <para>    
    It is compatible with the french examination "agregation de mathematiques".
    </para>
    
  </refsection>

  <refsection>

    <title>Quick Start</title>

    <para>
      This module provides a collection of 23 datasets. 
      In the following script, we extract the data for the dataset #10.
    </para>

    <programlisting>
      <![CDATA[
[x,txt] = getdata(10)
      ]]>
    </programlisting>

  </refsection>

